{"tid":589064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"311大地震七周年 AKB第67度派成員災區送暖","createTime":"2018-03-11T15:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T15:51:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"26ba07a0dcea332fba68fecfe3edf9d55e4a9c1a","tid":589064,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180311/large/1520746539_5911.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180311%2Flarge%2F1520746539_5911.jpg&h=0a33f6ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柏木由紀日前與隊友到福島探訪。<br />\n<br />\n今日3月11日是日本311地震七周年。2011年日本發生「311大地震」，帶來的人命傷亡及經濟損失，至今對日本人而言仍難補創傷。<br />\n<br />\n日本偶像組合AKB48多年來為振災不遺餘力，最近又派出成員到受影響各地探訪，柏木由紀、山本彩、北原里英、岡田奈奈等共24名成員分別到岩手、宮城、福島表演及掉念死難者，已經是AKB第67次到災區送暖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180311/large/1520746540_ab3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180311%2Flarge%2F1520746540_ab3f.jpg&h=10ed5785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180311/large/1520746542_09ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180311%2Flarge%2F1520746542_09ee.jpg&h=07b2a28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180311/large/1520746543_8a57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180311%2Flarge%2F1520746543_8a57.jpg&h=af75e93b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180311/large/1520746545_5264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180311%2Flarge%2F1520746545_5264.jpg&h=21257d8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b56ad84398fd7615e92dae7976fc5a667159bad","tid":589064,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"可否免費性愛"}]}